'''= an open source parallel corpus'''

URL = http://urd.let.rug.nl/tiedeman/OPUS/

=Description=

OPUS is an attempt to collect translated texts from the web, to convert and align the entire collection, to add linguistic data, and to provide the community with a publicly available parallel corpus. OPUS is based on open source products and is also delivered as an open source package. 


